<br>
I killed the 3 MOBs in the back cave and the 2 MOBs in the pit closest to the back cave.<br>
<br>
One thing to note. You should not have to run if two crystal spiders spawn. You simply need to med to full mana, then kill one spider as fast as you can, heal the pet, and hope for no bad resists. You must use an earth pet to take down three spiders, a 30 or 32 hitter.<br>
<br>
Here is the method I used to take down two spiders, and it worked everytime:<br>
1. Pulled with Malise.<br>
2. Send in damage shielded pet.<br>
3. /assist pet so you target the MOB it is hitting.<br>
4. Blaze<br>
5. Heal Pet<br>
6. /assist pet to retarget MOB he is hitting.<br>
7. Blaze <br>
8. Heal Pet<br>
9. MOB should be running by now, nuke it one last time to finish it. <br>
<br>
Make sure to cycle nukes. Use a lower lvl faster casting nuke to finish runner so it doesn't get out of range or site before you blast it down.<br>
<br>
If you get 3 spiders in back room, send in pet, then gate to Icewell zone. When they come to attack you, zone to Icewell keep. Chances are a guard or someone will kill at least one when they head back to spawn point.<br>
<br>
